          "new_post_text": "\"I'm with you - let's take a breath before we start freaking out. But can we also be real here? If our bottled water is tampering with our hormones, that's some next-level crazy stuff. We need solid proof, not just 'it's concerning but not yet conclusive'. I'm calling on health orgs to take this seriously and give us actual answers ASAP, not just vague promises of 'further investigation'. What's at stake here goes way beyond just a few scientists' opinions #waterqualitymatters #healthfirst\"",
